### Leo VI's Mass Vassal Directives - grey texticons
###
### Grey-tinted duplicates of the vanilla vassal-directive texticons, used to
### mark a vassal's directive icon as "exempt from automation" (a dimmed
### version of their normal directive icon) instead of the old cross overlay.
###
### Each entry copies the vanilla iconsize block verbatim (same texture, size,
### offset, fontsize - see game/gui/texticons.gui) and adds `color = color_dark_gray`.
### The color line inside iconsize is the vanilla-supported tint mechanism
### (e.g. texticons.gui:3417 color = "color_red"). color_dark_gray is a named
### format from game/gui/preload/textformatting.gui - chosen over color_gray,
### which was too subtle a dim against the gold directive art.
###
### Directive codes and their vanilla texticons are listed alongside the
### matching customizable-localization keys in leo_mvd_l_english.yml.

texticon = {
	icon = leo_mvd_grey_directive_none
	iconsize = {
		texture = "gfx/interface/icons/vassal_directives/no_directive.dds"
		size = { 35 35 }
		offset = { 0 11 }
		fontsize = 16
		color = "color_dark_gray"
	}
}
